dcterms:description: A dataset for clothing matching competition on TianChi platform. User historical behavior data is applied to make sequential recommendation. Users who purchase at least 30 times are included.
dcterms:title: Taobao

dcterms:description: A dataset for click prediction on Kaggle. It asks contestants to predict which recommended content on pages that each user will click. Only a sample version of the page views log data is applied, focusing on users with more than 10 views.
dcterms:title: Outbrain
